### Lab-Grown 1ct at Blue Nile

Blue Nile's 1ct lab-grown round selection starts under $600 and reaches into the mid-$1,000s for D-VVS1 IGI grades. [Browse all 1ct lab-grown rounds at Blue Nile →](https://www.bluenile.com/diamonds/round-cut?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)

**The 1ct verdict:** A D-VVS1 natural 1ct at Blue Nile runs $4,500–$5,000. The equivalent lab-grown is under $700. That's $3,800–$4,300 you keep in your pocket for a stone that is chemically, physically, and optically identical.

